revisions.description: Changed most product references from 'Compellent' to 'Dell Storage' and added level for StorageCenter under compellentEnterprise.
Added scScMgmtIP var to each trap.
Changed voltage values from unsigned to string, and added scEnclApiIndex.
Deprecated UsedSpace and TotalSpace (where GBs are calculated as 1000*1000*1000) and replaced them with vars calculated with GB = 1024*1024*1024.
Changed from Compellent enterprise number to Dell's.
Added IPv6 objects to CtlrTable and ScTable.
Changed how productIDGlobalStatus is handled. Added model and asset tags to scCtlrTable and scEnclTable. Added new tables scDiskConfigTable and scAlertTable.
Added traps organized by function rather than severity, and added new mib objects to support the new traps.
Cleaned things up to get rid of errors and warnings reported by MIB validators.
Applicable for Compellent Storage Center versions 5.0 and higher.
